full_text: I sponsored the Paycheck Protection Program Extension Act, a bipartisan bill led by my WA colleagues, @RepDerekKilmer and @HerreraBeutler, to expand and improve the program, and I’m going to keep working until every qualified business can access the assistance they need.

full_text: Right now Part B only covers care for serious conditions and people who are at a high risk for them. It doesn't cover yearly eye exams or access to glasses or contact lenses. Routine vision care should be covered under Medicare.

full_text: Teens who start using these medications often find them at home or at their friends’ homes. Don’t give them that opportunity. If a family member is using, get help and get opiates out of the house. And keep Narcan at home. These are powerfully addictive and lethal substances.
